Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.hardware

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Acquirer
    Acquirer is the class that is used to define all of the hardware for a robot's acquirer.
    Arm
    Arm is the class that is used to define all of the hardware for a robot's arm.
    Flipper
    Flipper is the class that is used to define all of the hardware for a robot's flipper.
    HardwareMain
    HardwareTank is the class that is used to define all of the hardware for a single robot.
    LegacyAcquirer
    Acquirer is the class that is used to define all of the hardware for a robot's acquirer.
    Mechanism
    Mechanism is an abstract class for all mechanisms on a robot.
    RCConfig
    Contains the constants for configuring hardware on the robot controller.
    Relic
    Relic is the class that is used to define all of the hardware for a robot's relic mechanism.
